id: pm-sz6w
title: "As an agent gating on pm health/validate, I want machine-executable remediation commands, so that I can auto-repair findings without hardcoding warning-code mappings"
description: "As an agent gating on pm health/validate, I want machine-executable remediation commands, so that I can auto-repair findings without hardcoding warning-code mappings"
type: Story
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: agent-ux,"area:observability",living-map,story
created_at: "2026-05-31T19:49:46.325Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-04T22:17:45.910Z"
author: maintainer-agent
acceptance_criteria: health --json emits per-check remediation map; validate --fix-hints emits executable pm commands per check; tests assert non-empty maps for known codes
parent: pm-5oj5
resolution: "Delivered machine-executable remediation across pm health (remediation_map) and pm validate (--fix-hints) from one shared registry, plus proactive settings-warning surfacing; closes child features pm-0hnu and pm-6m3y."
expected_result: Agents auto-repair pm health/validate findings without hardcoding warning-code mappings.
actual_result: health remediation_map + validate fix_hints both consume src/core/diagnostics/remediation.ts; 100% covered; full suite green.
